what it's about.


94
00:07:27.351 --> 00:07:30.100
I haven't read it yet.

95
00:07:31.893 --> 00:07:34.642
I'm not much of a reader, actually.

96
00:07:44.560 --> 00:07:45.975
How do I tell you?

97
00:07:47.018 --> 00:07:49.142
<i>Rivalry</i> is...

98
00:07:49.310 --> 00:07:50.850
Alright then...

99
00:07:51.893 --> 00:07:53.725
It's the story of two brothers:

100
00:07:53.893 --> 00:07:57.767
Manuel is dull, introverted,

101
00:07:58.018 --> 00:08:00.142
and his brother Pedro,
his older brother,


102
00:08:00.310 --> 00:08:04.184
is very sure of himself, and rich.

103
00:08:07.018 --> 00:08:10.309
1970: a country town.

104
00:08:11.310 --> 00:08:14.142
Manuel is driving his parents
down a road.


105
00:08:14.310 --> 00:08:16.100
It's night and he's drunk.

106
00:08:17.101 --> 00:08:19.350
He loses control and the car
rolls over and over.


107
00:08:19.518 --> 00:08:21.309
I hate drunks.

108
00:08:22.185 --> 00:08:25.475
The parents die in the crash.
Manuel is unhurt.


109
00:08:25.560 --> 00:08:27.975
Pedro, the other brother,
reports him to the police.


110
00:08:28.643 --> 00:08:29.725
Well done.

111
00:08:29.893 --> 00:08:33.391
Then Manuel is sentenced
to several years in prison.


112
00:08:33.560 --> 00:08:35.934
Meanwhile, Pedro goes on
with his life


113
00:08:36.101 --> 00:08:39.934
and has a relationship with Lucy,
a whore at the town brothel.


114
00:08:40.310 --> 00:08:42.475
Everyone is suspicious
of Pedro's luxuries.


115
00:08:42.726 --> 00:08:44.434
He has a foundry,

116
00:08:44.601 --> 00:08:47.392
but nobody believes that
the money comes from there.


117
00:08:47.560 --> 00:08:50.475
Years go by
and Manuel gets out of prison.


118
00:08:50.643 --> 00:08:54.392
Pedro knows his brother is free
but they never meet.


119
00:08:54.560 --> 00:08:58.684
Until one day Manuel goes to
the brothel and sleeps with Lucy.


120
00:08:59.018 --> 00:09:03.017
His brother finds out, proposes to Lucy
and offers her a life of luxury.


121
00:09:03.185 --> 00:09:04.642
Lucy says yes.

122
00:09:04.976 --> 00:09:07.225
Manuel sinks into a terrible depression.

123
00:09:07.393 --> 00:09:10.309
Then he finds out
that Lucy is pregnant.


124
00:09:11.101 --> 00:09:14.392
He begins to wonder
if the child is his.


125
00:09:14.560 --> 00:09:16.017
The baby is born.

126
00:09:16.185 --> 00:09:18.392
But is it his or not?

127
00:09:18.851 --> 00:09:20.059
Wait, I'll go on.

128
00:09:20.310 --> 00:09:23.309
One day Manuel steels himself
and goes to Pedro's house.


129
00:09:23.476 --> 00:09:24.809
He knocks on the door.

130
00:09:24.976 --> 00:09:26.309
Pedro opens up.

131
00:09:26.560 --> 00:09:28.100
Manuel sees Lucy with the baby

132
00:09:28.268 --> 00:09:31.434
in a scene of devastating ordinariness.

133
00:09:31.685 --> 00:09:34.559
Manuel asks, almost begs
to talk to his brother.


134
00:09:34.810 --> 00:09:38.767
The brothers walk around
the estate at night, in darkness.


135
00:09:39.143 --> 00:09:41.184
Manuel apologises to Pedro.

136
00:09:41.351 --> 00:09:42.642
Pedro relents.

137
00:09:42.810 --> 00:09:46.100
The brothers embrace
and cry like children.


138
00:09:46.518 --> 00:09:48.100
Because men do cry.

139
00:09:48.810 --> 00:09:50.142
I love it. It ends well.

140
00:09:50.310 --> 00:09:53.309
I like the ending.
The brothers have reconciled.


141
00:09:54.018 --> 00:09:56.017
Wait, it doesn't end there.

142
00:09:56.185 --> 00:09:58.184
There's still the ending.

143
00:10:45.393 --> 00:10:48.017
OFFICIAL COMPETITION

144
00:11:44.601 --> 00:11:46.184
Take care of it!

145
00:11:48.851 --> 00:11:51.725
Maestro, we meet at last.

146
00:11:51.893 --> 00:11:55.392
It'll be a real honour
to work with you.


147
00:11:56.893 --> 00:11:58.059
Thank you.

148
00:11:59.851 --> 00:12:00.934
Let's go.

149
00:12:02.435 --> 00:12:03.767
Well...

150
00:12:04.060 --> 00:12:05.934
First rehearsal, eh?

151
00:12:06.185 --> 00:12:08.475
Good luck, pal.

152
00:12:08.643 --> 00:12:10.184
You'll need it.

153
00:12:11.893 --> 00:12:13.225
Sure.

154
00:12:13.393 --> 00:12:16.975
So will you.
Don't get too confident.


155
00:12:17.643 --> 00:12:18.475
Coats.

156
00:12:20.310 --> 00:12:21.517
Thank you.

157
00:12:21.976 --> 00:12:23.225
Go ahead.

