Iván!

219
00:16:09.393 --> 00:16:10.392
Oh, jeez...

220
00:16:10.643 --> 00:16:12.850
Poor kids, poor kids.

221
00:16:13.018 --> 00:16:16.350
I want to return to what you said
about the character,


222
00:16:16.518 --> 00:16:18.309
that he doesn't want children.

223
00:16:19.101 --> 00:16:20.850
I think it's a major detail.

224
00:16:21.101 --> 00:16:23.267
So do I, it is.

