229
00:16:35.226 --> 00:16:37.361
Sorry, you gave it to me
on a platter.


230
00:16:37.560 --> 00:16:39.892
Yes, five with four
different women, yes.


231
00:16:40.060 --> 00:16:41.184
Do you have any Iván?

232
00:16:41.560 --> 00:16:42.767
Sorry?

233
00:16:43.018 --> 00:16:44.684
-Do you have any children?
-Yes, yes.


234
00:16:44.851 --> 00:16:47.059
One from my first marriage.

235
00:16:47.226 --> 00:16:49.767
He's grown up now, over 40.

236
00:16:49.935 --> 00:16:52.392
With Violeta,
we've been together for 28 years,


237
00:16:52.560 --> 00:16:54.309
we tried at the time,

238
00:16:54.476 --> 00:16:56.684
but now it's a little late.

239
00:16:56.851 --> 00:16:58.809
-I would have liked to.
-Okay.


240
00:16:59.601 --> 00:17:02.809
-Do you have...?
